   "info" : "<table width=\"100%\" summary=\"page for sanction\"><tr><td>sanction</td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">R Documentation</td></tr></table>\\n<h2>Multilateral Economic Sanctions</h2>\\n<h3>Description</h3>\\n<p>Data on bilateral sanctions behavior for selected years during the\\ngeneral period 1939-1983.  This data contains errors that have since\\nbeen corrected.  Please contact Lisa Martin before using this data for\\npublication.   \\n</p>\\n<h3>Usage</h3>\\n<pre>data(sanction)</pre>\\n<h3>Format</h3>\\n<p>A table containing 8 variables (&quot;mil&quot;, &quot;coop&quot;, &quot;target&quot;,\\n&quot;import&quot;, &quot;export&quot;, &quot;cost&quot;, &quot;num&quot;, and &quot;ncost&quot;) and 78 observations.\\nFor full variable description, see Martin, 1992. </p>\\n<h3>Source</h3>\\n<p>Martin, 1992</p>\\n<h3>References</h3>\\n<p>Martin, Lisa (1992).  <em>Coercive Cooperation: Explaining Multilateral\\nEconomic Sanctions</em>, Princeton: Princeton University Press.\\n</p>\\n",
